snippet.title: James Dearden Bush
snippet.description:
Musician, intuitive healer, breathwork facilitator, sound healer, and journeyer on the kundalini path. Sharing my ambient guitar music, crystal singing bowl sound baths, and videos relating to my kundalini awakening and spiritual journey. Other topics on this channel include; spirituality, shamanism, planetary healing, herbalism, plant medicines, consciousness, and the global awakening/ascension process. All my music and sound baths are tuned to the healing frequency of 432Hz and are created with love and healing intent.

I offer spiritual guidance sessions and support for people going through a kundalini awakenings, intuitive hands on healing, and sound healing sessions. I also hold group breathwork sessions, group sound baths, and live music ceremonies and events. For more information please visit my website at https://www.jamesdeardenbush.com

*This YouTube channel was previously named RevolutionLoveEvolve
